  <content contentuid="h9df706a1g5be2gfe23ge441g6b093266fc2f" version="1">Deva</content>
  <content contentuid="h69b871cfg8f7eg4104g96d6g32a8a150f515" version="3">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="h00e1f1a6g2759g128cg3d43g485cee099af4" version="1">Aasimar are mortals who carry a spark of the Upper Planes within their souls. Whether descended from an angelic being or infused with celestial power, they can fan that spark to bring light, healing, and heavenly fury.</content>
  <content contentuid="h18822cb0gea17g437dgbfedg0be88122dd3e" version="3">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="h6b1e2915gcc0fgfc3cg45aagda9e59566c9e" version="1">Aasimar are mortals who carry a spark of the Upper Planes within their souls. Whether descended from an angelic being or infused with celestial power, they can fan that spark to bring light, healing, and heavenly fury.</content>
  <content contentuid="heb23c599geb3fg21f8g4ce2g039327781d51" version="1">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="h4f11fd38ge37agd9b8g1232gbfc102dcfad7" version="1">Endowed with a divine lineage, aasimar represent the physical and mental experience of other mortal creatures elevated. In the long uncertain night of Faerûnian life, they burn like pale inspiring torches.</content>
  <content contentuid="h8e30e5f4g5bafgfa50g4ec8g50d88c930b29" version="1">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="hc6a27b52g65bcg6c92geb9fg912e998fd18e" version="1">Aasimar are mortals who carry a spark of the Upper Planes within their souls. Whether descended from an angelic being or infused with celestial power, they can fan that spark to bring light, healing, and heavenly fury.</content>
  <content contentuid="h61a7f42agaa2dg0a37g0201gffeada6c93c9" version="2">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="hb25fcb9bg5458gd5b6g3c63g80e8058420e9" version="2">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="h153d4254gf6c4gc42fg3900g112b87a47121" version="2">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="h3798f0c8gde93g7745gf2f5g43fdab986e6b" version="1">Aasimar</content>
  <content contentuid="h40a69736440c471b8d3faf80aec618ef8d87" version="1">Dream Visitor</content>
  <content contentuid="hb80cd039993d49b196e7500136da8a768962" version="1">Dream Visitor</content>
  <content contentuid="hf4ec8b07gbb48g860ag940cg471cbb0c435a" version="1">Celestial Resistance</content>
  <content contentuid="h163a49eegcf6bgc3f9g2e3egeb269dc99438" version="1">You have &lt;LSTag Tooltip="Resistant"&gt;Resistance&lt;/LSTag&gt; to Radiant and Necrotic damage.</content>
  <content contentuid="h25b023fcg8a95gd791g3c80gc964b39db3f4" version="1">Healing Hands</content>
  <content contentuid="h65b347754b8e42b4b64bfc1ba1824068e8ge" version="1">Imbue your touch with celestial healing energy to restore [1].</content>
  <content contentuid="hcd20662agb3fcg53acgca2agf8b40321c4bb" version="1">Celestial Revelation</content>
  <content contentuid="h23c8425670774559a85e7b55efbd49513b84" version="1">Undergo a transformation to unleash the celestial energy within yourself. Once per turn before the transformation ends, you can deal an additional [1] or [2] with an attack or spell depending on the revelation chosen.</content>
  <content contentuid="h7992312fga293g775cge97bg491e8b0da29d" version="1">Heavenly Wings</content>
  <content contentuid="hcf33cb9fgbfb4g5ab5gda84g279f3d187fd2" version="1">Spectral wings sprout from your back temporarily, granting you &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Projectile_Fly_Aasimar"&gt;flight&lt;/LSTag&gt;. Once on each of your turns, you can deal an extra [1] when you deal damage with an attack or a spell.</content>
  <content contentuid="hc49a7eb1g2518g1f75gb1c3gd3771db4d36d" version="1">Heavenly Wings</content>
  <content contentuid="hf43c82efc8f9449a9514189d4b756bd25aeg" version="1">Has the ability to &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Projectile_Fly_Aasimar"&gt;fly&lt;/LSTag&gt; on a pair of spectral wings and deal an additional [1] on your attacks or spells once per turn for the duration of the transformation.</content>
  <content contentuid="h16ff007agc8e5g1460ge6bagad83a17cf3c6" version="1">Inner Radiance</content>
  <content contentuid="h3f9c29704f644f8fa7af4e5e54d625c2788b" version="1">Searing light temporarily radiates from your eyes and mouth, shedding a bright light for [1]. At the end of each of your turns, each creature within [1] of you takes [2].&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Once on each of your turns, you can deal an extra [2] when you deal damage with an attack or a spell.</content>
  <content contentuid="he4fdb4eag8159g33d2g28fbg084b08c991b5" version="1">Inner Radiance</content>
  <content contentuid="h519a84daaa0b4325b536aeb7d08a055cbf2e" version="1">Searing light radiates from you, lighting up the darkness and dealing [1] to any creature within [2] of you at the end of your turns.</content>
  <content contentuid="h8dbd870fgb3fbg4d26g909fg64ed22e6934d" version="1">Inner Radiance</content>
  <content contentuid="h0ba307db8b994135b72f605d7c349e5c48ca" version="1">Creature is engulfed by a consuming radiance that deal [1] per turn.</content>
  <content contentuid="h37bb7092g98d2gb21bg2c48gf7a30cf32074" version="1">Necrotic Shroud</content>
  <content contentuid="h0537e2ee7b8c4b1bb3e2e951f8887959fa18" version="1">You become engulfed by overwhelming darkness, and flightless wings sprout from your back. Enemies within [1] must succeed a Charisma &lt;LSTag Tooltip="SavingThrow"&gt;Saving Throw&lt;/LSTag&gt; or become &lt;LSTag Type="Status" Tooltip="FRIGHTENED"&gt;Frightened&lt;/LSTag&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Once on each of your turns, you can deal an extra [2] when you deal damage with an attack or a spell.</content>
  <content contentuid="h7ea0632dg738bgc4a3g605bg71f7efc1e939" version="1">Necrotic Shroud Aura</content>
  <content contentuid="hb0ac953dg4af5g2172g5ff7g633f22600c9a" version="1">Can possibly &lt;LSTag Type="Status" Tooltip="FRIGHTENED"&gt;Frightened&lt;/LSTag&gt; nearby enemies with its terrifying revelation.</content>
  <content contentuid="hcbff9a3cgd27bgb506g729dgfaf1650ca6c5" version="1">Necrotic Shroud</content>
  <content contentuid="hdc660e51ga1e5g3674gff09ga474b192d63c" version="1">This creature's proximity to an aasimar's necrotic shroud fills it with fear. It will become &lt;LSTag Type="Status" Tooltip="FRIGHTENED"&gt;Frightened&lt;/LSTag&gt; unless it succeeds a Charisma &lt;LSTag Tooltip="SavingThrow"&gt;Saving Throw&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>
  <content contentuid="hab598497743942ec8b88ad68cb71a05562cg" version="1">Necrotic Shroud</content>
  <content contentuid="h3161a5597caf4eaa960739a82cf9aff398bc" version="1">Deal an additional [1] on your attacks or spells once per turn for the duration of the transformation.</content>
  <content contentuid="h49a7422818974fb8aabde2c917e75107g1gb" version="1">Dismiss Transformation</content>
  <content contentuid="h3c20bcc12c1041ddbc48234ca7b591f21975" version="1">Dismiss your celestial transformation and return to your normal form.</content>
  <content contentuid="h079a1233gbd04g2ac1g660fgfbf979c291ac" version="1">Celestial Revelation: Radiant</content>
  <content contentuid="h4c18040fg1f7egf501g6614g545d46d51cb9" version="1">Deal an extra [1] once per turn.</content>
